# proglang-keywords/html.twlist
#
# language: HTML (HTML5 element names + global / common attribute names +
# common attribute values).
# source: html.spec.whatwg.org (Living Standard). MDN HTML Elements
#   reference cross-checked. Vendor / framework extensions (Bootstrap,
#   custom-element prefixes) are NOT included.
# notes: HTML is largely no-underscore. Hyphenated tokens (data-*,
#   aria-*, the role names) admit as single WORDs. The handful of
#   "data-foo" / "aria-foo" entries below are listed bare; the `data-`
#   and `aria-` prefixes themselves cover the family idiomatically.

# ----- Document / sectioning -----
html_html          html
html_head          head
html_body          body
html_title         title
html_meta          meta
html_link          link
html_base          base
html_style         style
html_script        script
html_noscript      noscript
html_template      template
html_slot          slot
html_header        header
html_footer        footer
html_main          main
html_section       section
html_article       article
html_nav           nav
html_aside         aside
html_address       address
html_hgroup        hgroup
html_doctype       doctype

# ----- Text content -----
html_h1            h1
html_h2            h2
html_h3            h3
html_h4            h4
html_h5            h5
html_h6            h6
html_p             p
html_hr            hr
html_pre           pre
html_blockquote    blockquote
html_ol            ol
html_ul            ul
html_li            li
html_dl            dl
html_dt            dt
html_dd            dd
html_figure        figure
html_figcaption    figcaption
html_div           div

